OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774444274
OL,3,CUK Inflation remained steady in
OL,4,CFebruary - before the Iran war started
OL,6,FUK inflation remained steady last
OL,7,Fmonth but households could face
OL,8,Fanother "twist" to the cost-of-living
OL,9,Fstory in the months ahead due to war
OL,10,Fin the Middle East, according to
OL,11,Fexperts.
OL,13,FThe rate remained at 3% in February,
OL,14,Faccording to figures released by the
OL,15,FOffice of National Statistics on
OL,16,FWednesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
