OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774444274
OL,3,CUK Inflation remained steady in
OL,4,CFebruary - before the Iran war started
OL,6,FThe rate of Consumer Prices Index
OL,7,F(CPI) inflation has been gradually
OL,8,Feasing back towards the Bank of
OL,9,FEngland's 2% target level since last
OL,10,Fsummer.
OL,12,FBefore the US and Israel attacked Iran
OL,13,Fon February 28, experts were
OL,14,Fpredicting that inflation would return
OL,15,Fto the target of 2% this year.
OL,17,FHowever, the Bank of England has said
OL,18,Frecent increases in wholesale energy
OL,19,Fcosts would delay the return of CPI
OL,20,Finflation to target, as it was already
OL,21,Fseeing higher fuel prices.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
