CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774444274
OL,3,CUK Inflation remained steady in
OL,4,CFebruary - before the Iran war started
OL,6,FIt is now expecting inflation to be
OL,7,Faround 3% in the second quarter of
OL,8,F2026, up from the 2.1% that had been
OL,9,Fforecast in February.
OL,11,FMeanwhile, grocery experts are warning
OL,12,Fthat UK households could face food
OL,13,Finflation above 8% within months if
OL,14,Fdisruption caused by the Iran war
OL,15,Fpersists.
OL,17,FIGD (Institute of Grocery
OL,18,FDistribution) said the conflict in the
OL,19,FMiddle East could result in food
OL,20,Finflation more than doubling by the
OL,21,Fsummer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
