OL,3,CUK Inflation remained steady in
OL,4,CFebruary - before the Iran war started
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FCommenting on Wednesday's inflation
OL,12,Ffigures for February, ONS Chief
OL,13,FEconomist Grant Fitzner said:
OL,14,F"February's inflation figures have,
OL,15,Ffor the first time, included
OL,16,Fsupermarket scanner data, replacing
OL,17,Fmany of our physically collected
OL,18,Fprices, marking a significant
OL,19,Fimprovement in our measurement and
OL,20,Funderstanding of changing prices
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
