OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774444274
OL,3,CUK Inflation remained steady in
OL,4,CFebruary - before the Iran war started
OL,6,F"After last month's slowdown, annual
OL,7,Finflation was unchanged in February as
OL,8,Fvarious price movements offset each
OL,9,Fother.
OL,11,F"The largest upwards driver was the
OL,12,Fprice of clothing, which rose this
OL,13,Fmonth but fell a year ago. This was
OL,14,Foffset by falls in petrol costs, with
OL,15,Fprices collected before the start of
OL,16,Fthe conflict in the Middle East and
OL,17,Fsubsequent rise in crude oil prices.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
