PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774444274
OL,3,CUK Inflation remained steady in
OL,4,CFebruary - before the Iran war started
OL,6,F"A fall in the cost of alcoholic
OL,7,Fdrinks due to promotional activity,
OL,8,Fcompared with a rise last year, was
OL,9,Falso a downward driver, while little
OL,10,Fchange in food prices, again compared
OL,11,Fwith a small rise this time last year,
OL,12,Fadded further downward pressure."
